The South African State Theatre JOHANNESBURG - To commemorate the eighth anniversary of the Marikana massacre, the State Theatre will be uploading Marikana The Musical on Youtube. The musical looks at the tragic events of that week. Police shot and killed 37 miners in August 2012. READ: Organiser of Marikana rally murdered, says NUM Actor Aubrey Poo plays the lead character in the production. Poo explained the significance of the play. In the month of August, we celebrate women in South Africa. Courtesy #DStv403